# Kubernetes Security Audit Report

Client: Demo Environment  
Date: Feb 2026  

---

# Findings

## Critical

Privileged containers detected

Impact:
Container escape possible

Recommendation:
Disable privileged mode

---

## High

Secrets accessible to default service account

Recommendation:
Implement least privilege RBAC

---

## Medium

No network policies

Impact:
Lateral movement possible

---

# Tools Used

kubectl  
kube-bench  
kubescape  
trivy  

---

# Overall Risk

HIGH
